description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 MIN TABATA AB Workout - No Repeat Exercises, Tabata Cardio Style, Low Impact' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.
